{
  "texts": [
    "LeaderboardTo ensure the reproducibility and comparison of various student cognitive modeling models, we provide a public leaderboard.",
    "As illustrated in Fig. 7, there are two major features: Task Selection and Detailed Leaderboard.",
    "The former requires users to specify elements such as task type and dataset.",
    "The latter provides a comprehensive comparison between models in the form of graphs and tables based on specified elements.To support all users in uploading their experiment results, we provide a portable processing flow.",
    "In EduStudio, each experiment eventually forms a specific log directory (as depicted in Table 4)."
  ]
}